t race over King at a Tyr Pro Series meet in San Antonio.\", \"from\": 2188, \"to\": 2281, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 2273, \"end\": 2280, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Antonio_Vivarini\", \"score\": 0.6052776286044584, \"rank\": 0.37825667743840774, \"text\": \"Antonio\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Antonio_Vivarini\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Antonio_Vivarini\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"Thursday\", \"from\": 2191, \"to\": 2199}, {\"ngram\": \"Jacoby\", \"from\": 2201, \"to\": 2207}, {\"ngram\": \"a 100m breast race\", \"from\": 2212, \"to\": 2230}, {\"ngram\": \"King\", \"from\": 2236, \"to\": 2240}, {\"ngram\": \"a Tyr Pro Series meet\", \"from\": 2244, \"to\": 2265}]}, {\"sentence\": \"King still retained the nation's best time this year from a meet in January.\", \"from\": 2282, \"to\": 2358, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"King\", \"from\": 2282, \"to\": 2286}, {\"ngram\": \"the nation's best time\", \"from\": 2302, \"to\": 2324}, {\"ngram\": \"a meet\", \"from\": 2340, \"to\": 2346}, {\"ngram\": \"January\", \"from\": 2350, \"to\": 2357}]}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"I am about where I was last year at this time and ended up swimming really well at nationals (in 2023),\\\" King said.\", \"from\": 2360, \"to\": 2476, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"this time\", \"from\": 2397, \"to\": 2406}, {\"ngram\": \"nationals\", \"from\": 2444, \"to\": 2453}, {\"ngram\": \"King\", \"from\": 2466, \"to\": 2470}]}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"I am where I need to be.\\\"\", \"from\": 2477, \"to\": 2503, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"NBC Sports' Andy Dougherty contributed to this report from San Antonio.\", \"from\": 2505, \"to\": 2576, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 2505, \"end\": 2515, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/NBC_Sports\", \"score\": 0.9999999634219428, \"rank\": 2.7211380180578802e-08, \"text\": \"NBC Sports\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"h